      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ABOVE THE LAW (1) is now in the Beer & Carpenter yard and a win looks imminent fourth-up. Used up early from the wide gate with a fighting second over 1600m at Warwick Farm in a Super Maiden on April 15. Finally drawn a decent gate and expected to get off the mark. MAKO (5) total forgive from the wide gate third-up with an ordinary last over 1400m at Hawkesbury. Since fitted with a 1207m trial at Warwick Farm. Nicely placed to turn things around as he gets out in trip. DEMMO DERMY (3) has shown more consistency this time in, and he gets map favours again today. Stretched out quickly to the 1600m second-up with a game on-pace fifth over 1600m at Hawkesbury. Will push forward and figure prominently. SOLID (7) showed early speed from a good draw on resumption before folding up late to finish third over 1400m at Hawkesbury. Cross-over nose band and winkers go on. Schiller sticks and keep safe.",
